---
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Me: Max Parisi" description="About Max Parisi">
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title="About"
				tagline="Thanks for stopping by. Read below to learn more about myself and my background."
			>
				<img
					width="1553"
					height="873"
					src="/assets/skiing.jpg"
					alt="Max skiing"
				/>
			</Hero>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						Hi! I'm Max, a developer, maker, and photographer who loves turning ideas into reality.
						Whether I'm writing code, designing hardware, or working behind a camera, I enjoy creating
						projects that are both functional and meaningful. I'm naturally curious and enjoy learning
						how things work, which has led me to explore everything from web development and
						electronics to networking and smart home automation.
					</p><br>
					<p>
						I learn best by building. Rather than simply reading about new technologies, I enjoy
						experimenting, solving problems, and refining projects until they work the way I imagined.
						Every project teaches me something new, whether it's improving my programming skills,
						discovering a more efficient solution, or gaining experience with a new tool or technology.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						I have experience developing full-stack web applications with JavaScript and Node.js,
						creating responsive user interfaces and reliable backend services. I'm passionate about 
						embedded systems and electronics, designing projects with ESP32 and Arduino 
						microcontrollers, sensors, displays, and custom hardware. Beyond programming, I enjoy
						photography, 3D printing, and CAD design, allowing me to bring together digital and physical
						creations into complete, polished projects.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Interests</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						I enjoy building projects that solve real problems or create unique experiences. Some of
						my favorite projects include custom web applications, smart home integrations with Home
						Assistant, electronics and IoT devices, interactive websites, and tools that combine
						hardware with software. I like exploring new ideas, refining them through iteration, and
						creating projects that are both technically interesting and enjoyable to use.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	img {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}
</style>
